      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The sheriff spat on the floor, his voice rough. \"They ain't got the sense to know what's good for 'em, and they sure as hell ain't got the brains to lead.\" The businessman scoffed, shaking his head dismissively. \"Some folks are just built for one thing, and they ain't built for this kind of progress.\" The judge agreed with a chilling certainty. \"It's the natural order, plain and simple; some people belong where they belong, and we're just keeping the peace by making sure that stays true.\"",
